      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Federal Deposit Insurance Act to provide the same treatment for covered bonds as for other qualified financial contracts to which a depository institution is a party when such institution is in receivership or conservatorship, and for other purposes.</title>
